Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯 亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯之死给身为母亲的泰莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃至整个泰坦尼亚都带来了巨大冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督被再次确认为泰坦尼亚的公敌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过那孩子若有个三长两短 绝不饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为那孩子才貌双全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心生嫉妒 所以才见死不救的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你 害死了他…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还我亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就要 还我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩儿定要擒住杀害亚瑟斯的凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听凭母亲大人处置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我发誓！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里发誓 哲力胥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以生命和名誉起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若违背方才的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就诅咒你一辈子 哲力胥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了就快点行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔柯夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我传令下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现方修利之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活捉之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供情报者重重有赏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不准杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要留活口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官遵命 马上去办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾厄之芽必须趁早摘除
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公主看来 我很清闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我能留在这里看你工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会打扰你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请您暂退吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何贵干？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下次最高会议上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能举荐我负责讨伐不逞之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个叫方修利的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了亚瑟斯伯的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想亲手抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯的仇 我要亲手报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利应该是全体泰坦尼亚的公敌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但哲力胥卿和他的母亲只是出于私怨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人望的亚瑟斯伯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚也甩掉了一个包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 却连一个爱子成痴的母亲都制不住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「哲力胥是宇宙第一猛将」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵们都这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看来人外有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 他的母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓血肉亲情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会使事情节外生枝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有父亲在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必感同身受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时 方修利提督从正直老人号上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飞前应该还在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说提督就喜欢搞突然失踪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他还在为没能救莉拉而耿耿于怀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督可是泰坦尼亚的敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然公然和泰坦尼亚为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有高枕无忧之地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇蝎遍野 不得不防
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是希望所在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能把你交给泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见你最后一面 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明才要开始的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好容易见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多想说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星卢塔西 艾斯特拉德府
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星リュテッヒ エストラード邸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现任藩王手下 我们没法飞黄腾达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样对皇帝陛下尽忠 都已无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 就只有指望艾斯特拉德侯爵阁下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾斯特拉德·泰坦尼亚侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エストラード・タイタニア侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了阁下 也为了我们的共同利益
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不惜一切手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿人在艾里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回天城尚需时日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为军务大臣的我正手握近卫军指挥权
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要举事 现在正是不二良机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚历亚伯特卿怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他多半会和渚士朗卿同进退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我方动作够快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能占得先机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于哲力胥和渚士朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二者去其一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 若两者都不在的话如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此话怎讲 艾斯特拉德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位知道渚士朗卿奉藩王之命远赴艾曼塔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此话当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午就会正式决定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只剩哲力胥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要设饵巧妙 那家伙必然中计
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自诩足智多谋的狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自诩军略无双的饿狼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁二兽离穴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是将亚术曼赶下藩王宝座
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我方建立新体制的不二良机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星卡萨比安卡 宇宙港
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星カサビアンカ 宇宙港
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萨比安卡吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已被泰坦尼亚统治三十年之久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民生活却平静如常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}カレン
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后找到工作了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人 此话当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我手下得来的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已探明杀害亚瑟斯的仇人所在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为亚瑟斯报仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落后之人严惩不贷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿的舰队出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他得悉了方修利的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不等最高会议作出决定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一意孤行出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随他去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能成功便罢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若失败 孤自有处置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你什么时候从艾里亚来这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个月 不 已经三个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾里亚已经那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后发生了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没活干了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 认识的大叔帮我混上了货船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷渡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 别说得这么难听嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我挣钱了会还他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样 是乘偷渡船过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命近卫军向水晶宫进发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操之过急了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于有机会大展才能了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 请您从长计议
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将责任推给宫廷贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们一网打尽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密 事到如今还说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被吓破胆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一再劝我政变的不正是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况有变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在举事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人也无法取代现任藩王…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有权对我指手画脚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休得放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早在你出生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是泰坦尼亚的重臣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请恕孩儿无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人会自毁未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 我还有什么未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去只能终生屈于亚术曼之下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对同父异母的弟弟俯首称臣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于那样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经忍无可忍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已包围水晶宫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1224,923)\fad(500,500)}维尔达纳帝国内务大臣 萨格登
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1224,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヴァルダナ帝国内務大臣 ザグデン
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军已占领各主要目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到进展居然如此顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(728,923)\fad(500,500)}维尔达纳帝国民政大臣 努尼艾司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(728,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヴァルダナ帝国民政大臣 ヌニエス
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用法得当 那个老废物也能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}维尔达纳帝国司法大臣 赫拉瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヴァルダナ帝国司法大臣 ヘラウァー
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就来宣布新体制的建立吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解您的心情 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓获三名叛乱份子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓获叛军司令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在没空和你争论
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 能请您再听我说两句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在亚术曼麾下忍辱偷生 学到一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被负面思考所支配的人终将一事无成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到明天就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上去叫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以叛国罪嫌疑逮捕艾斯特拉德·泰坦尼亚侯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕书在此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请随我们走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若敢抵抗 我们就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其余三名主谋已被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是宫廷贵族的独断专行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密 给我枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 您要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:19:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔达纳的叛乱已被镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主谋全部逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 艾斯特拉德侯爵受殃及而死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯特拉德侯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情不明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现方修利一事是叛乱煽动者散布的虚假情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可认为是调虎离山之计
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为悼念艾斯特拉德侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命全员服丧三日如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道现在一切话语都显得苍白无力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我只能借话语来安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是出使艾曼塔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没想到会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 一切都是有预谋的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾厄之芽必须趁早摘除
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲散布虚假情报 自以为骗过了哲力胥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实他不过是在你掌心起舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了一扫维尔达纳的叛乱煽动者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到连艾斯特拉德侯都…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得有点过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 叛乱份子被一举剿灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事是出于渚士朗卿的一己独断
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或亚术曼藩王也知情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能交由后世史学家判断了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.77,0:24:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萨比安卡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想像中要好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.61,0:24:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚的魔爪应该伸不到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.39,0:24:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先在这里悠闲几天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.04,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(649,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}如沧海一粟


